ActImpact Assessment Act
PrecisAppointment of TERRENCE HUBBARD of Ottawa, Ontario, to be interim President of the Impact Assessment Agency of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eight months or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective November 28, 2021.
